txt.en: The Yule Festival is a time of celebration and merriment. Come and join the festivities in Frostbluff and drink, eat, and be merry.\n\nHappy Yule!
Visit the delightful land of Frostbluff where all things winter and all things special are happening.  Come quickly!\n\n
